Third-Party Software Notices
============================

This project (Apache-2.0) incorporates the following third-party components:


libxsm3 - Xbox Security Method 3
---------------------------------
Source: https://github.com/InvoxiPlayGames/libxsm3
License: LGPL-2.1-or-later
Location: src/lib/libxsm3/
Copyright: (C) 2022-2023 InvoxiPlayGames

Xbox 360 console authentication (XSM3) implementation. Statically linked into
firmware. Full source is provided in src/lib/libxsm3/ with modifications noted
in xsm3.c per LGPL-2.1 Section 2(b). The complete LGPL-2.1 license text is at
src/lib/libxsm3/LICENSE.

Contains ExCrypt crypto primitives (excrypt_*.c/h) from:
  https://github.com/emoose/ExCrypt (BSD-3-Clause)
With DES implementation referencing:
  https://github.com/fffaraz/cppDES
And SHA-1 implementation referencing:
  https://github.com/mohaps/TinySHA1
